To run:
rails s -b $IP -p $PORT

Changing database structures will need you to configure Heroku db. Here are the steps: 
heroku run rake db:reset --app menage
heroku run rake db:migrate --app menage
heroku apps 

Commiting to git:
git add .
git commit -m "Message"

When merge errors:
git clean -df 
git checkout -- .

